  "body": "<!-- Please only use this template for submitting enhancement requests -->\r\n\r\n**What would you like to be added**:\r\ndisplay EphemeralStorage usage with 'kubectl describe node' , like;\r\n```\r\nAllocated resources:\r\n  (Total limits may be over 100 percent, i.e., overcommitted.)\r\n  Resource           Requests    Limits\r\n  --------           --------    ------\r\n  cpu                0 (0%)      0 (0%)\r\n  memory             0 (0%)      0 (0%)\r\n  ephemeral-storage  100Mi (1%)  100Mi (1%)\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Why is this needed**:\r\nephemeral-storage is a standard ContainerResources like CPU and Mem now. but now we don't display it in the node state. \r\n```\r\nvar standardContainerResources = sets.NewString(\r\n\tstring(core.ResourceCPU),\r\n\tstring(core.ResourceMemory),\r\n\tstring(core.ResourceEphemeralStorage),\r\n)\r\n```\r\n<!-- DO NOT EDIT BELOW THIS LINE -->\r\n/kind feature\r\n/sig cli\r\ncc @soltysh ",
